The paper focuses on data augmentation techniques for deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The proposed method involves optimizing the augmentation policy distribution along with network training, which falls under the category of reinforcement learning and optimization (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and deep learning (cs.DL) techniques.
